    "pages": [
        {
            "text": "Akai had no shoes. Other children her age \u00a0 \u00a0 had shoes.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9494.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "\"It is difficult to play without shoes,\" said Akai \u00a0to her mother.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9492.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "\"Akai,  I think it is time for you to have shoes,\" said mother.\u00a0.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9493.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Mother woke up Akai \u00a0 early the next morning.\u00a0 \u00a0.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9496.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Akai and her mother went to the market.\u00a0.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9495.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "They went into a shoe shop. Mother bought shoes for Akai.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9497.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "At night,  Akai thought about her new shoes.\u00a0.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9499.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Akai put on her new shoes.\u00a0.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/10444.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Akai thought about how she would show off her shoes.\u00a0.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9498.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Akai wore her new shoes again. She danced around the room.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9502.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "\"Akai,  you must not wear shoes in bed,\" said mother.\u00a0.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9501.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Akai was so happy to have shoes for the first time.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9500.png"
        },
